page.title: 07North Street,Pottery,Garage.
page.content: The{pottery}is in Freezes farm yard. It has been there 8 years.The lady there makes domestic ware and animal models.She sells her models throughout East Anglia.{Westrope's Garage}in North Street occupies an acre. They sell 75 new Nissan and 150 second hand cars a year.The things that are usually wrong with cars is that they have crashed. They sell sweets, paraffin, polish, paints, cigarettes, coal and petrol, as well as servicing and repairing peoples' cars. Further along North Street there is a small new development of houses called{The {Chase.}There are 9 houses, altogether and 5 of them are finished. Each house has 4 bedrooms, a lounge, dining room, kitchen, utility room, a cloakroom, and 2 bathrooms. The builder is Mike Welbey.
